Looking to offer VPS renting services to your customers? you have came to the right place, Modules Factory is pleased to announce the release of Proxmox Module offering a fully automated VPS selling system utilizing the powerful Proxmox Technology in the back-end, with unlimited Clusters/nodes support and almost same VM config features as seen in Proxmox gui, solution comes with configoptions and addon products for extra scalability.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
